name: PNC-Visit number
description: Visit within 24 hours is 1st visit, similarly in 3 days is 2nd visit and in 7 days is 3rd visit. Visit other than mentioned days should be kept in "other visit"

name: PNC-Visit type
description:
Women who delivered at BH should have at least one (1st) PNC visit. c/s cases should have 1,2 and 3rd PNC visit. 
Transfer in - Women delivered other than BH and referred to BH for PNC visit. 
Other -  Women who self-visited / not referred.

name: PNC-HIV tested
description: HIV status needs to be known only if the women was not tested previously during delivery or before 3 months.
